nodes.text: Gift Giving Wookiees was a painting made sometime after the Battle of Yavin. It was part of a series of five paintings, alongside Kashyyyk at Night, Gift Giving Wookiees, Red Robed Wookiee, and Wookiee with Pups, that were made for the festivities of Life Day. The painting in question depicted a Wookiee standing in a prideful position. It was supplied during the events of an annual Life Day celebration on Kashyyyk.
Proud Wookiee, alongside Kashyyyk at Night, Gift Giving Wookiees, Red Robed Wookiee and Wookiee with Pups, were supplied during the 2006 Wookiee Life Day festivities.
